								<li>• Avoid 6-9 AM window during heavy rains (visibility issues)</li>
								<li>• Electric vehicles = SAFER (better traction, lower center of gravity)</li>
								<li>• Expressway = well-maintained, better than city routes during rains</li>
								<li>• Pre-booking essential (weather tracking, flexible timing)</li>
							</ul>
							<p class="mt-3"><strong>WhatsApp Booking:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/919145499009?text=I%20need%20a%20monsoon%20season%20cab%20from%20Pune%20to%20NMIA" class="text-green-600 font-semibold">+91 91454 99009</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="mt-4">
							<Button asChild class="w-full sm:w-auto">
								<a href="https://wa.me/919145499009?text=I%20need%20a%20monsoon%20season%20cab%20from%20Pune%20to%20NMIA">Book Monsoon-Ready Cab</a>
							</Button>
						</div>
					</CardContent>
				</Card>
			</div>

			<!-- Table of Contents -->
			<div class="not-prose my-8">
				<Card>
					<CardHeader>
						<CardTitle>Complete Guide Contents</CardTitle>
					</CardHeader>
					<CardContent>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
							<li><a href="#route-conditions" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">1. Pune-NMIA Route Conditions During Monsoon</a></li>
							<li><a href="#timing-adjustments" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">2. Timing Adjustments & Buffer Planning</a></li>
							<li><a href="#vehicle-safety" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">3. Why Electric Vehicles are Safer in Rain</a></li>
							<li><a href="#waterlogging" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">4. Waterlogging Zones & Alternate Routes</a></li>
