										<li>• Flight: 8:30 AM at NMIA</li>
										<li>• Weather: Light continuous drizzle, no heavy rain forecast</li>
										<li>• Standard pickup: 6:00 AM (2.5 hours before flight)</li>
										<li>• Monsoon adjustment: 5:45 AM (add 15 min buffer)</li>
										<li>• Actual journey: 2h 10min (reached 7:55 AM, comfortable 35 min airport buffer)</li>
										<li>• <strong>Result:</strong> On time, stress-free journey</li>
