									<ul class="space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
										<li>• Flight: 10:00 AM at NMIA</li>
										<li>• Weather: Very heavy overnight rain, waterlogging in Pune city</li>
										<li>• Standard pickup: 7:30 AM (2.5 hours before flight)</li>
										<li>• Monsoon adjustment: 6:00 AM (1.5 hours early due to city waterlogging risk)</li>
										<li>• Actual: Slow city exit (30 min), expressway good, total 3h 15min</li>
										<li>• Reached: 9:15 AM (45 min buffer, perfectly timed)</li>
										<li>• <strong>Result:</strong> Early start compensated for city conditions, made flight with buffer</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
